data.description: Welcome to your new Ranch style home in the desirable Pine Tree Farms neighborhood of Feasterville-Trevose, Bucks County! This corner property is comfortably shaded and gives you a calming sensation from the soothing sounds of the cool breezes through the trees and the serenades from the various birds and cicadas. As soon as you approach this beautiful home, you'll appreciate the newly installed roofing (Jan 2023) and siding (Jan 2022)! Park your cars in the driveway or in the attached 1-car garage with inside entrance access to a convenient powder room/utility room combo with washer/dryer, gas boiler with winter/summer hookup, and some storage shelving, adjacent to the Family room with ceiling fan laminate flooring & sliding doors to the covered porch where you can sit outside and enjoy all of your naturistic surroundings. There is an additional front Living room entrance if you prefer, with wood flooring, ceiling fan, and wood burning Fireplace, adjacent Dining area with ceiling fan, and a full modern Kitchen with wood cabinetry, marble counter-tops, farm sink, gas range/oven, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator. The hallway offers a coat closet and a separate storage closet, a modern 3pc bathroom with floating vanity and vessel sink, shower/tub combo, and toilet, and then 3 spacious Bedrooms, each with wood flooring, freshly painted, and ceiling fans with remote control. Please take a minute to view the video tour and then schedule your in-person appointment, today!
